precis:
Enactment of the FORM OF PROXY (BANKS) REGULATIONS which are designed to
replace the current regulations in an effort to streamline and harmonize
federal proxy rules and to address technical problems identified by the
Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
